About Us

Arcane Technologies PLC positions itself as a trusted partner for technology solutions, specializing in sales force automation software, customer relationship management, point of sales management, and trade marketing management services. Our expertise is geared towards enhancing sales productivity for businesses.

Our Vision

We Envision This

Our vision is to be the leading technology solutions provider in East Africa and beyond. We aspire to create a positive impact on society by empowering businesses with innovative and reliable technology solutions. We value excellence, integrity, innovation, and customer satisfaction.

Our Mission

We Provide This

Our mission is to provide our customers with high-quality technology solutions and consulting services that meet their needs and goals. We aim to deliver solutions that optimize business operations, reduce costs, and improve efficiency. We strive to build long-term relationships with our customers and partners based on trust and mutual benefit.

Our History

What We Sell

Our expertise on data center, security, end-user computing solutions and IT services networking,custom training, and internet solutions aimed at enhancing productivity and competitiveness. We also distribute  telecom service and products like SIM card, Airtime vouchers, high quality Routers and Mifi’s, different brand of high end Mobile apparatus . and we import provide high quality IT products like Desktops,Laptops,Servers and Printers. We provide tailored integrated video surveillance systems and  access control systems , and We provide enterprise Software and our own Sales force Automation Software with full Route to Market service that includes comprehensive management tools to boost sales productivity and customer relations.

Portfolio

Who We Work With

We have worked with some of the biggest names in the industry and have earned a reputation for excellence. Some of our clients include: Castel Group, Indomie Noodles, SBG Industry PLC, PetroEthio, Sheraton Addis, Dashen Bank S.c, McKinsey & Company, Samsung, Fontera Brands, Puratos, Pepsico, Alvima We also have different level of partnerships with some of the leading technology companies in the world such as Huawei, Canon, Epson, HP, Honeywell, Safaricom, and Logitech.
